# pyproject-tmpl

## features

1. pytest
2. pre-commit
3. darker for code format
4. ruff for lint
5. commitlint for commit message format

## 使用方式

- 初始化环境：`./scripts/setup`

- 执行测试：`uv run -m pytest`

- 启动服务：`uv run main.py`

- 构建发布：`./scripts/publish`


